OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP election
OL,4,Ccampaign bus with trip from Dundee to
OL,5,CAberdeen
OL,7,FJohn Swinney is due to launch the
OL,8,FSNP's election campaign bus in Dundee
OL,9,Fon Saturday, as he seeks to highlight
OL,10,Fhis policy on bus fares.
OL,12,FIn the party's manifesto, Mr Swinney
OL,13,Fpledged to cap bus fares at #2 across
OL,14,FScotland.
OL,16,FThe First Minister will ride the SNP
OL,17,Fbus ` which has livery reading "On
OL,18,FScotland's side" ` from Dundee to
OL,19,FAberdeen, saying that such a journey
OL,20,Fwould cost #2 on public buses if the
OL,21,Fpolicy is implemented.
OL,26,@yD@`OUzD@PO]
