FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776474192
OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP election
OL,4,Ccampaign bus with trip from Dundee to
OL,5,CAberdeen
OL,7,FThe SNP says people making the journey
OL,8,Fwould save #7.60 under their plans.
OL,10,FScots will go to the polls on May 7.
OL,12,FMr Swinney said: "I am looking forward
OL,13,Fto campaigning in every part of
OL,14,FScotland between now and polling day.
OL,16,F"The SNP is the only party fighting to
OL,17,Fwin in every part of Scotland ` and I
OL,18,Fintend to be First Minister for all of
OL,19,FScotland.
OL,26,@tD@ROUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776474192
OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP election
OL,4,Ccampaign bus with trip from Dundee to
OL,5,CAberdeen
OL,7,F"It is obvious that the cost of living
OL,8,Fis the defining issue of this campaign
OL,9,F` whether fuel prices, food prices or
OL,10,Fenergy bills, people are really
OL,11,Fstruggling. And the SNP will not sit
OL,12,Fback ` we will take action."
OL,14,FHe continued: "Today, I am travelling
OL,15,Ffrom Dundee to Aberdeen and, under the
OL,16,Fcurrent system, that journey could
OL,17,Fcost people almost #10. With a re-
OL,18,Felected SNP Government, it will be #2.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@\O]vD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
