FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776474192
OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP election
OL,4,Ccampaign bus with trip from Dundee to
OL,5,CAberdeen
OL,7,F"At a time when people are struggling,
OL,8,Fpublic transport needs to be
OL,9,Faffordable ` people need to be able to
OL,10,Fget to their work and to get out and
OL,11,Fabout. That is what I will ensure
OL,12,Fhappens with the SNP's #2 bus fare
OL,13,Fcap."
OL,15,FA pilot scheme to cap bus fares at #2
OL,16,Fwas implemented in parts of Scotland
OL,17,Fearlier this year.
